---
import Seo from "../../../lib/seo/metadada.astro"
---
<Seo title="Mensagem Enviada | Baú de Promoções" noindex type="article"></Seo>

  <style>
    /* --- NOVA IDENTIDADE VISUAL --- */
    :root {
      --primary-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff4b4b 0%, #ff9000 100%);
      --bg-body: #f5f5f5;
      --text-dark: #1a1a1a;
      --text-muted: #666666;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --card-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }

    body {
      background-color: var(--bg-body);
      color: var(--text-dark);
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    /* --- CARTÃO DE SUCESSO --- */
    .success-card {
      background: var(--white);
      padding: 60px 40px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      /* Removemos a borda neon e adicionamos sombra suave */
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.03); 
      max-width: 450px;
      width: 90%;
      box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
      animation: popIn 0.5s ease-out;
    }

    @keyframes popIn {
      0% { transform: scale(0.9); opacity: 0; }
      100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
    }

    /* --- ÍCONE CHECK --- */
    .icon-check {
      width: 90px;
      height: 90px;
      /* Gradiente Laranja/Vermelho */
      background: var(--primary-gradient);
      color: var(--white);
      font-size: 45px;
      line-height: 90px; /* Centraliza verticalmente */
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin: 0 auto 30px;
      display: block;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(255, 75, 75, 0.3); /* Brilho laranja */
    }

    /* --- TIPOGRAFIA --- */
    h1 {
      color: var(--text-dark);
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    p {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* --- BOTÃO DE VOLTAR --- */
    .btn-home {
      display: inline-block;
      background: var(--primary-gradient);
      color: var(--white);
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 15px 40px;
      border-radius: 50px; /* Formato Pílula */
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(255, 75, 75, 0.2);
    }

    .btn-home:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(255, 75, 75, 0.4);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="success-card">
    <span class="icon-check">✓</span>
    <h1>Sucesso!</h1>
    <p>Sua mensagem foi enviada para o Baú de Promoções. Responderemos em breve no seu e-mail.</p>
    <a href="/" class="btn-home">Voltar para o Início</a>
  </div>

</body>
</html>